Package window

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompoundedFrame
    This class is the frame which is used throughout the entire Compounded game.
    Credits
    This class contains the panel that displays the game credits.
    Goodbye
    This class contains the panel that is displayed when the user wishes to exit.
    Instructions
    This class contains the panel that is displayed when the user wishes to view the game instructions.
    MainMenu
    This class displays the main menu of the Compounded game.
    Options
    This class contains the panel that is displayed when the user wishes to view the game options.
    SplashScreen
    This class contains the splashscreen panel which fades in an image.
